	e thrills. The world is not enough\, but Seattle is!Merging the raw excite
	ment and hilarity of classic Drag revues\, the glamour of burlesque and ca
	baret shows\, and a bit of performance art for your nerves\, GRINDHAUS is 
	an unforgettable experience with your host Bosco at the wheel.Line Up:Bosc
	oNaomi SmallsAjaKing MolassesCali ColbyClara VoyanceMiss Texas 1988\nThis 
