	ut notice. No refund will be owed if an Opening Act is changed or canceled
	. Doors times subject to change Tickets may not be resold or offered for r
	esale. If we suspect tickets have been purchased for resale purposes only\
	, we reserve the right to void or cancel the tickets without refund. Ticke
	ts obtained from unauthorized sources may be invalid\, lost\, stolen or co
	unterfeit and if so\, are void.\nPrice: $42.3 - $42.3\n\nhttps://www.ticke
	tweb.com/event/earlybirds-club-the-crocodile-tickets/14742193\n\nFrom The 
	Crocodile
